description:
Assassin's Creed Shadows is now out on Nintendo Switch™ 2!

 Your journey through the breathtaking world of Feudal Japan begins today! Unleash your inner Assassin as Naoe, a stealthy shinobi, and strike from the shadows. Or take command as Yasuke, a towering samurai, and dominate the battlefield. 

Weather you're a new player or a returning shinobi ready for more, Feudal Japan awaits you! Enjoy cross-progression and touchscreen support in all menus - including world map, store and hideout - whether you're at home or on the go!

Learn more: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
Watch more: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBnrd5k2F2IOOjoz62wdQntPrz6D0xjWq

author: Ubisoft
description:
Get the Tenfold Pursuit Battle Pass to unlock more than 100 tiers of rewards including a 14-day early access to the new PMR90A2 weapon, exclusive new skins for Ace, IQ or Mira, new Delta Packs, R6 Credits and more. Available in-game and at https://rainbow6.com/battlepass

About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

author: Ubisoft
description:
Tom Clancy's The Division 2 new season, ""Mutiny"", is coming on December 2nd, Agents!

A mutiny is taking root in the ranks of the True Sons, Gear Up agents, the uprising begins.

“Mutiny” introduces a new set of Modifiers, seasonal events including the Winter event and special collaborations, Veteran rewards, friend referral, and the arrival of a new feature: NPC Companion.

About The Division 2:
Tom Clancy's The Division 2 is a shooter RPG with a thrilling campaign fully playable in co-op and multiple PVP modes.

In The Division 2, save your country in Washington, DC, and in the Warlords of New York expansion, hunt down Aaron Keener, a former Agent who has taken control of New York.

#Ubisoft #TheDivision2
